        "  - <Medication name> — <dose> <route> <frequency> (<max/day if relevant>) — <1 short prescriber blurb: key contraindications/adjustments>\n"
        "  - <Non-med advice> — <short actionable instruction>\n"
        "- Alternatives:\n"
        "  - <Medication name> — <dose> <route> <frequency> (<max/day if relevant>) — <1 short prescriber blurb>\n"
        "  - <Medication name> — ...\n"
        "- Testing:\n"
        "  - <If needed now: refer in-person urgent care/ED; otherwise none now + when to escalate>\n"
        "- Return precautions:\n"
        "  - <specific red flags + timeframe>\n\n"
